8", "uri": "https://scontent-sin11-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036602_243585652000211_899556208890795274_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_aid=0&_nc_ohc=IemFb1KJCMsQ7kNvgHOyD3H&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin11-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDWfHv7M6Kn2E_c6F2wzYiu__CZq1LRAaW5htsU3-5BGA&oe=677E6022"}, {"file_name": "EarthQyest.png", "id": "3512913448957611", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031395_3512913452290944_8432013420749195897_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bATv5hsajvUQ7kNvgHR59NF&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDs7eeUk-GGOPN-7PJNPHIM73jf5pypwkwvcMdxmlcY6Q&oe=677E4E01"}, {"file_name": "EarthQyest.png", "id": "834517198252006", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003282_834517204918672_5256638514144330387_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vK5nLJFS0bAQ7kNvgGhBgna&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBimGUjLBlqpw7a_6spSu5rguR7LodZtEzBl-cwf5VcVA&oe=677E643D"}, {"file_name": "EarthQyest.png", "id": "1723712434760725", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031546_1723712438094058_2534245311378872057_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=87VQOAzmsx8Q7kNvgFGkyPM&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCKfUDi3w2BR4xCzPsaF0TE-GvHo0zQBSynF2zsGwn3WA&oe=677E5805"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "EarthQyest.png", "id": "1078756446490659", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982454_1078756449823992_493302951635196042_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0ZWD_Fz7fsQQ7kNvgGoWV8f&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBusA1xGNpb81d4KY_TbYz04xSkHSevPHkHjZu8t2MPMA&oe=677E5869"}, "display_name": "EarthQuest", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Quest 2 Game made in Unity with the Cesium Package using the Google Earth Photogrammetry 3d Tiles.\n\n---------------------------------------------\nUPDATE v10 !! : hopefully the MOST STABLE and the Update that Simplified the Flight Controlling Mechanic the Most, v10 is meant to finalize the heavy game development for a month or two, however, fixes and improvements will still come if there are any needs for it. this Update adds Controller SUPPORT!!! basically the rest is self explanatory, the update also fixes a bug that due to the collider removal and raycast to prevent going through mesh, even if the Earth's Mesh was not visible in Space, it was still there, so the raycast stopped Player Movement when trying to go down, this was Fortunately FIXED!,\n\nv10.2: the Controllers are now Able to Type on Keyboard to Search and Teleport to a specific Place on Earth, and fixed a bug where the space bar touch collider was small,\n\nv10.3: when you pressed on some specific ui buttons, the code gave an error and every other ui stopped working since they had the same script. this was fixed. 3d Earth Generation to have better quality and faster performance, also loading faster and in larger quantity, we'll have to know if that's the case, if not we'll have to redo the changes in v10.4 :/, another improvement was that flight speed adjustment based on altitude was not efficient, and sometimes caused teleporting instead of flying smoothly, fixed !\nhttps://youtu.be/6s-jkai4_mA\n---------------------", "short_description": "geography teaching hand tracking passthrough VR app/game on Quest 2 Quest Pro, and Quest 3"}]}, "developer_name": "Bowie/Electrum", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rfelQCihEG-gjgHBpxfy5Kd52Y2-Vj9LTwpGWsoWFZ0/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vkc-TWH53X4qPwdf9J-erq8Pl_xvB_sYFUK2jHG94TY/edit?usp=sharing", "publisher_name": "Bowie/Electrum", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ZXJHOoHOgvJ6mK5_gHPoqyyQy8B6IKGn?usp=drive_link", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "726368587961803"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1703886060119133"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 4, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1197247534802870"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1218595455967648"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "966363545148360"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "865031525282969"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1197247534802870"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1722030957, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1197247534802870"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8712922375504085", "version": "4352"}, "id": "997411404840848", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8712922375504085"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v43.5 is HERE !\n\n# Mini-map Updates\n\n- Discover nearby Community Street Views, See Official Street View Coverage on a larger scale, and more with the new Street View Coverage Overlay Toggle !\n\n- Improved user-marker design \ud83d\udd3a \n\n- Reengineered zooming: zoom motion is no longer linear and feels much more natural, and altitude-based auto zoom is more intuitive and responsive overall \ud83d\udd0e\u2728\n\n- Added new zoom-in level, offering the ability to zoom closer in for even more details about your location \ud83d\udccd \n\n# Additional\n\n- Varied smaller improvements, UI refinements, and bug fixes\n\n- Refined UI Color-Scheme, featuring a fresher, more \u201cpearly\u201d blue !\n\n- Small optimizations for performance\n\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\n\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small - ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1735923364, "id": "8712922375504085", "version": "4352", "version_code": 4352, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8712922375504085"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v43.5 is HERE !\n\n# Mini-map Updates\n\n- Discover nearby Community Street Views, See Official Street View Coverage on a larger scale, and more with the new Street View Coverage Overlay Toggle !\n\n- Improved user-marker design \ud83d\udd3a \n\n- Reengineered zooming: zoom motion is no longer linear and feels much more natural, and altitude-based auto zoom is more intuitive and responsive overall \ud83d\udd0e\u2728\n\n- Added new zoom-in level, offering the ability to zoom closer in for even more details about your location \ud83d\udccd \n\n# Additional\n\n- Varied smaller improvements, UI refinements, and bug fixes\n\n- Refined UI Color-Scheme, featuring a fresher, more \u201cpearly\u201d blue !\n\n- Small optimizations for performance\n\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\n\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small - ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1735841518, "id": "8707958746000448", "version": "4350", "version_code": 4350, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8712922375504085"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "-\nv43 is HERE !\n\n# Better Bookmarks Management\n\n- You can now better organize your bookmarks with the ability to empty unused slots\n\n- To empty a slot, simply load that slot ( be at that saved position ) and press \u2018Save Location\u2019; Now, instead of overwriting, you will be able to empty it \ud83e\uddf9 !\n\n# Introducing Autocompleted \u2018Search For Place\u2019 locations !\n\n- Autocompleted \u2018Search For Place\u2019 location results !\n\n# Additional \n\n- New magical Soundtrack in EarthQuest\u2019s music library\n\n- Improved Render Accuracy for Human-Size (no performance costs)\n\n- Some optimizations were made to Fog Rendering, expect small performance improvements when Fog is enabled.\n\n- Small varied improvements, UI refinements, bug fixes\n\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small - ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1735577567, "id": "8691369870992669", "version": "4301", "version_code": 4301, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8712922375504085"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "-\nv43 is HERE !\n\n# Better Bookmarks Management\n\n- You can now better organize your bookmarks with the ability to empty unused slots\n\n- To empty a slot, simply load that slot ( be at that saved position ) and press \u2018Save Location\u2019; Now, instead of overwriting, you will be able to empty it \ud83e\uddf9 !\n\n# Introducing Autocompleted \u2018Search For Place\u2019 locations !\n\n- Autocompleted \u2018Search For Place\u2019 location results !\n\n# Additional \n\n- New magical Soundtrack in EarthQuest\u2019s music library\n\n- Improved Render Accuracy for Human-Size (no performance costs)\n\n- Some optimizations were made to Fog Rendering, expect small performance improvements when Fog is enabled.\n\n- Small varied improvements, UI refinements, bug fixes\n\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small - ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1735404464, "id": "8681071378689185", "version": "4300", "version_code": 4300, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8712922375504085"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "-\nv42.5 is here !\n\n# Street View improvements\n\n- Optimized Street View system, allowing fastest possible loading times on any type of Street View Imagery\n\n- Slightly smoother performance when a panorama is first being loaded\n\n# Introducing Featured Locations !\n\n- Renamed `Saved Locations` to `Bookmarks`\n\n- Enjoy 27 featured breathtaking places, highlighted on the first 1-4 pages of `Bookmarks`.   |   Note: these will only take your unoccupied slots\n\n- Saving to an occupied slot will now ask for confirmation, seamlessly preventing accidentally replacing it\n\n# Additional \n\n- New Soundtrack !! - https://youtu.be/6tvgcSUaQ5Q\n\n- Safely allocated slightly more memory for loading 3D Maps\n\n- AI can now translate ANY TEXT from Street View Imagery !\n\n- Maximum AI recording time should no longer limit longer recordings, it is now extended from 30s to 80s\n\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small - ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1735140811, "id": "8665275326935457", "version": "4255", "version_code": 4255, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}